text: Fungus Rock, sometimes known as Mushroom Rock, and among the Maltese as Il- Ġebla tal-Ġeneral (), is a small islet in the form of a massive lump of limestone at the entrance. It is on the coast of Gozo. Fungus Rock is located at and falls near the town of San Lawrenz. ==References== Category:Islands of Malta
title: Fungus Rock
